Highland Creek Partners















  Highland Creek Partners is a unique investment firm focused on acquiring and growing a single small to medium sized company through active management and a world-class Board of Directors





A Better Way To Exit
Highland Creek provides owners with an attractive alternative to traditional exit options. We offer fair terms that are tailored to a seller’s unique situation and ensure the success of our sole investment by supplying a full-time management team and world-class Board of Directors.





Grow Your Business, Preserve Your Legacy
Our long-term investment horizon enables us to focus on sustainable growth and value creation. We will work relentlessly to keep your customers happy while retaining your employees and helping them grow with the business. Have confidence that your legacy is in good hands.





World-class Team
Our team has been carefully assembled to grow a single small to medium sized business. Our investor group includes 19 current and former CEO/Presidents and 4 Ernst & Young Entrepreneur of the Year award winners. Highland Creek's Managing Partners bring experience from private equity, management consulting, operations, corporate finance and entrepreneurship.





























 









